Sunday September 22nd 2013 9:58 pm -04:00,Remember that square brackets indicate a list so you cant mix them with parentheses.Cap_song_repetition is a function not a variable or list. The function uses the list and the song as its parameters. So it takes the playlist and the song and alters the list according to the while loop. The idea is to try one at a time and see which works. As for errors you cant print something before you define what it is.  You will get errors for the ones that are wrong so you should expect some errors.  What exactly are you putting into IDLE? Im not good enough at this to analyze whats going on with your code but I would review the posts above and run the code in the visualizer so you can see what is happening. Hope this helps., Resolved,1
